summary: Sithis retreat: A player home for people who like the Dark brotherhood, and want to be a real Dark brotherhood initiate!
descriptionHtml:
Sithis retreat: A player home for people who like the Dark brotherhood, and want to be a real Dark brotherhood initiate!
You can find the key to the home in the Falkreath sanctuary, but if you are already settled down in the Dawnstar sanctuary, there will be a key there as well!


NOTE: If the Dark brotherhood initiate leaves you, he will stay wherever you left him, so let him leave you at home!

Features:
Alchemy lab
Arcane enchanter
Smithing ability
An extra follower
A fireplace
author: Diablo3547
